Sample From Telemetry Object

A sampled dataset can have models fitted much quicker. This is used to reduce waiting time in developing code that involved time consuming modeling processes. After code is tested and stablized, full size dataset can be used.

sample_tele(tele, m)

Arguments

tele

telemetry object
m

sample size. m even spaced points are taken from data.

Value

sampled telemetry object

Examples

library(ctmm)
data(buffalo)
sample_tele(buffalo[[1]], 100)
